{
  "stem": "597.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "From Polish you have to go on Russian, and in Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It's-- It's very hard, but we strived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I managed it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I made it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And then the war came between Russian-- Russia and-- and Poland-- I mean, Russia and Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "That was a bad experience that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They bombed the city.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I had to run away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "My father-- when I came back home, there was worrying about me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I came back in a military car.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And-- And the 70 kilometers was so far away, that time, because the aeroplanes from the Germans was on [INAUDIBLE] bombing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And-- And-- And very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "A lot of people perished that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And I finally came back home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "So my-- my father was so happy to see me, and mother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "They thought I'm dead already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And I was-- was waiting till the German came in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "The German came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I want to go away deep in Russia, but my father didn't let us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "You are girls.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "It's very dangerous to go for you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And you're young.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "So you stay here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "Whatever it's gonna be with us, it will with you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "So that's why I left-- was left with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "Waiting for the Germans, and the German came in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "Started to German, and the German came in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So right away, and we saw already that some terrible things happened to us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Already was starting to grab us to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't even give us food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They give us only 10 out of this 20 grams of bread a day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was a very little piece of grain.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If only 20 grams is like a-- a fifth of a kilogram. 100 grams is a kilogram.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And 20 grams is the like dark bread, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
